          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The secondary beam of 6He ions was produced by the",
                " bombardment of a thick (350 mg/cm2) beryllium target",
                " with a 43 MeV/n 13C primary beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 400 um CH2 foil was used as a hydrogen target.",
                "The data were collected in two runs."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " The reaction products of interest were detected by",
                "  an array of two dE x dE x E telescopes mounted on",
                "  two arms movable in the horizontal plane.",
                " Each telescope consisted of two silicon strip",
                "  detectors (area of 60 x 60 mm2, thickness of 400 um,",
                "  29 identical 2 mm strips in each detector) and",
                "  a 20 mm thick CsI(Tl) crystal 65 x 65 mm2 in area.",
                " The calibration of the strip detector was performed",
                "  using a 226Ra source."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The errors include the contributions from",
                "  statistical errors and the inaccuracy of the",
                "  efficiency simulations (including, for in-transfer",
                "  data, also the small solid angle uncertainties",
                "  caused by the two extreme assumptions made for the",
                "  5He decay).",
                " Total uncertainty is about 30%, for which the main",
                "  contribution to this value is caused by the beam",
                "  monitoring errors."
              ]
            }
          ],
